data.actual_result: "End of results" does not show up on every search
data.expected_result: "End of results" shows up on every search
data.short_description: "End of results" does not appear for every search word in gif picker
data.steps_to_repro: - Open the gif picker in a channel - Search for a word, such as "maho" - Scroll to the bottom of the resulting gifs and observe the option to return to the top - Search for a different word, such as "kurisu" - Scroll to the bottom of the resulting gifs again and look for the option to return to the top
